text: The following lists events that happened during 2014 in Cape Verde. ==Incumbents== *Prime Minister: José Maria Neves *President: Jorge Carlos Fonseca ==Events== *Oceanpress, newspaper of the island of Sal published its first edition *September 22: the 6th José Maria Neves Cabinet began *November 23: Start of the 2014–15 eruption of Fogo ==Sports== *CS Mindelense won the Cape Verdean Football Championship ==References== Category:Years of the 21st century in Cape Verde Category:2010s in Cape Verde Cape Verde Cape Verde
title: 2014 in Cape Verde
